cat("This message is sent from a peaceful civilization curious about a world beyond their own. Our people are curious about the existence of life in other parts of the universe, as we do not have the technology to traverse beyond our solar system. As a people we want to know about your life and what technology you have discovered. The curiosity of our people knows no bounds, we are very willing to trade knowledge of the universe and what we have compiled. We await your response and are on constant standby for you to visit us and discuss the universe.")